{"tid":2331500,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"點解Macbook嘅Magsafe沒有成為主流普及化嘅硬件必需???","createTime":"2020-12-18T23:10:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T11:35:58.000Z","uid":284284,"like":3,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"395dd9d5551c720712b3ff0f8d2e287bcea354b2","tid":2331500,"uid":284284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T23:10:19.000Z","msg":"買咗部新laptop （Windows）<br />\n之前用開係2015年有magsafe嘅macbook<br />\n覺得magsafe係理所當然，冇人留意，但係超級好嘅feature<br />\n<br />\n跟住再望返我呢部新laptop<br />\n點解仲係用緊20年前嗰種laptop圓形電源插頭嘅？<br />\n有人踢到條電線部laptop飛落地下似乎係遲早會發生嘅事？<br />\n<br />\n想問點解到咗2020年<br />\nMacbook嘅Magsafe竟然沒有成為主流普及化嘅硬件必需?<br />\n點解 multi-touch, usb-c, hdmi, ssd 呢d就變咗主流<br />\n而magsafe就冇，甚至連Apple自己都唔再出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35237d870087d45a41a590c4e4bf0cc9aa747ff","tid":2331500,"uid":11927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T23:27:13.000Z","msg":"要好用，取代唔到先會留低"},{"pid":"aed005a4fcb8542edb5542bde9b9303dad5a9fd6","tid":2331500,"uid":9387,"like":21,"dislike":9,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T23:47:56.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">有人踢到條電線部laptop飛落地下似乎係遲早會發生嘅事<br />\n</span><br />\n用左十幾年laptop都未發生過同未見過<br />\n<br />\n想叉電果陣搵唔到線就大把 所以全世界先將type C變主流<br />\n<br />\n一個咁低機率會發生嘅事點解你會expect全世界都會在乎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"118a7272198075745d9c72fb9afd3dd07c38dda6","tid":2331500,"uid":916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T00:20:31.000Z","msg":"專利同成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840239f9ec53ff24ac4a2f45a660e5dc3e5bb56f","tid":2331500,"uid":88886,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T00:25:10.000Z","msg":"窗口機不嬲都係低級科技20幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj